    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Afrotrombicula machadoi (Taufflieb, 1962), holotype. A, dorsal aspect of idiosoma; B, ventral aspect of idiosoma; C, dorsal idiosomal seta; D, preanal seta. Abbreviations as in Fig. 5. Scale bars: 100 µm (A, B), 20 µm (C, D)." ;
