    dc:description "FIGURE 14. Afrotrombicula machadoi (Taufflieb, 1962), holotype. A, scutum; B, dorsal aspect of gnathosoma; C, ventral aspect of gnathosoma; D, leg I, genu–tarsus; E, leg I, trochanter–telofemur; F, leg II, trochanter–tarsus; G, leg III, trochanter– telofemur; H, leg III, genu–tarsus. Abbreviations as in Fig. 6. Scale bars: 50 µm (A, D–H), 20 µm (B, C)." ;
